<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>EntityRegistry<sp/>and<sp/>EntityManager</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>**EntityRegistry**<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>single<sp/>source<sp/>of<sp/>truth<sp/>for<sp/>entity<sp/>lifecycle.<sp/>It<sp/>manages<sp/>handle<sp/>allocation,<sp/>version<sp/>tracking,<sp/>and<sp/>entity<sp/>validation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>**EntityManager**<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-level<sp/>API<sp/>combining<sp/>registry<sp/>and<sp/>component<sp/>storage:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">EntityRegistry<sp/>registry;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">EntityManager<sp/>manager(registry);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Create<sp/>entity</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto<sp/>entity<sp/>=<sp/>manager.create();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Attach<sp/>components</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto*<sp/>transform<sp/>=<sp/>manager.emplace&lt;TransformComponent&gt;(entity,<sp/>glm::vec3{0.0f});</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto*<sp/>velocity<sp/>=<sp/>manager.emplace&lt;VelocityComponent&gt;(entity);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Check<sp/>and<sp/>retrieve<sp/>component</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">if<sp/>(manager.has&lt;TransformComponent&gt;(entity))<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>auto*<sp/>t<sp/>=<sp/>manager.get&lt;TransformComponent&gt;(entity);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Remove<sp/>single<sp/>component</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">manager.remove&lt;TransformComponent&gt;(entity);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Destroy<sp/>entity<sp/>(removes<sp/>all<sp/>components<sp/>and<sp/>invalidates<sp/>handle)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">manager.destroy(entity);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
